     (

SELECT
    ROUND(numerator / denominator) AS Pharmacy_PMPM
FROM (
    SELECT
        t1.contract_name,
        t1.payer_name,
        t1.plan_name,
        t1.numerator,
        t2.denominator
    FROM (
        SELECT
            p.contract_name,
            p.payer_name,
            p.plan_name,
            SUM(visit_amount) AS numerator
        FROM l5.visit_pcp ao
        LEFT JOIN l5.payer p
            ON p.payer_master_id = ao.payer_master_id
        LEFT JOIN l5.date dt
            ON dt.month_of_date = ao.month_of_visit
        LEFT JOIN l5.pcp m
            ON m.org_hierarchy_master_id = ao.org_hierarchy_master_id
        WHERE visit_type = 'Medication'
          AND month_of_date  ${Date}
        GROUP BY
            p.contract_name,
            p.payer_name,
            p.plan_name
    ) t1
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT
            p.contract_name,
            p.payer_name,
            p.plan_name,
            COUNT(empi) AS denominator
        FROM l5.attribution z
        LEFT JOIN l5.payer p
            ON p.payer_master_id = z.payer_master_id
        LEFT JOIN l5.date dt
            ON dt.month_of_date = z.month_of_attribution
        LEFT JOIN l5.pcp m
            ON m.org_hierarchy_master_id = z.org_hierarchy_master_id
        WHERE month_of_date  ${Date}
        GROUP BY
            p.contract_name,
            p.payer_name,
            p.plan_name
    ) t2
      ON t1.contract_name = t2.contract_name
     AND t1.payer_name = t2.payer_name
     AND t1.plan_name = t2.plan_name
) final
WHERE ${Conract_var}

SELECT DISTINCT

FROM (

    MD5(ap.payer_id || ':' || ap.plan_id) AS payer_master_id,
    ap.plan_name,
    ap.org_hierarchy_master_id,
    COALESCE(ep.num, 0) ${default_file_name} 12000 AS numerator,
    COALESCE(ap.den, 0) AS denominator
  FROM (
    SELECT
      COUNT(empi) AS den,
      payer_id,
      plan_id,
      plan_name,
      month_of_attribution AS month_of_measurement,
      org_hierarchy_master_id
    FROM l5.attribution_patient
    WHERE ${Conract_var}
    GROUP BY
      month_of_attribution,
      payer_id,
      plan_id,
      plan_name,
      org_hierarchy_master_id
  ) ap
  LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT
      month_of_visit,
      payer_master_id,
      org_hierarchy_master_id,

    FROM l5.ed_opp_patient
    GROUP BY
      month_of_visit,

LEFT JOIN l5.pcp pc

SELECT DISTINCT  
  ROUND(CAST(SUM(numerator) / NULLIF(SUM(denominator), 0) AS FLOAT),2) AS ip_per_1000
FROM (
  SELECT
    ap.month_of_measurement,
    MD5(ap.payer_id || ':' || ap.plan_id) AS payer_master_id,
    ap.plan_name,
    ap.org_hierarchy_master_id,
    'utilization' AS metric_type,
    'ip_per_1000' AS metric,
    'IP/1000' AS metric_name,
    COALESCE(ep.num ${default_file_name} 12000, 0) AS numerator,
    COALESCE(ap.den, 0) AS denominator
  FROM (
    SELECT
      COUNT(empi) AS den,
      payer_id,
      plan_id,
      plan_name,
      org_hierarchy_master_id,
      month_of_attribution AS month_of_measurement
    FROM l5.attribution_patient
    WHERE ${Conract_var}
    GROUP BY payer_id, plan_id, plan_name, org_hierarchy_master_id, month_of_attribution
  ) ap
  LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT
      payer_id,
      plan_id,
      org_hierarchy_master_id,
      DATE_TRUNC('month', visit_start_date) AS month_of_visit,
      COUNT(visit_id) AS num
    FROM l5.readmit_patient
    GROUP BY payer_id, plan_id, org_hierarchy_master_id, DATE_TRUNC('month', visit_start_date)
  ) ep
  ON ep.month_of_visit = ap.month_of_measurement
  AND ep.payer_id = ap.payer_id
  AND ep.plan_id = ap.plan_id
  AND ep.org_hierarchy_master_id = ap.org_hierarchy_master_id
  WHERE ap.month_of_measurement ${Date}
) t;

SELECT 
    ceil(((visit_count / member_months) ${default_file_name} 12000),2)AS imaging_utilization_per_1000
FROM (
    SELECT 
        SUM(v.visit_count) AS visit_count
    FROM l5.visit_pcp v
    LEFT JOIN l5.payer p ON v.payer_master_id = p.payer_master_id
    LEFT JOIN l5.pcp pc ON v.org_hierarchy_master_id = pc.org_hierarchy_master_id
    WHERE ${Conract_var}
        AND v.month_of_visit ${Date}
        AND v.visit_type = 'Professional'
        AND v.visit_sub_type IN (
            'Imaging Others', 'CT Imaging', 'MRI Imaging',
            'Professional - Radiology - CT', 'Professional - Radiology - MRI', 
            'Professional - Imaging Others', 'Professional - Radiology - Mammography', 
            'Professional - Radiology - Nuclear', 'Professional - Radiology - PET', 
            'Professional - Radiology - Therapeutic', 'Professional - Radiology - X Ray'
        )
) t1
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT 
        COUNT(a.empi) AS member_months
    FROM l5.attribution a
    LEFT JOIN l5.payer p ON a.payer_master_id = p.payer_master_id
    LEFT JOIN l5.pcp pc ON a.org_hierarchy_master_id = pc.org_hierarchy_master_id
    WHERE  ${Conract_var}
        AND a.month_of_attribution ${Date}
) t2 ON TRUE;

with attr as  ( select count(${default_file_name}) member_months  from L5.attribution_patient  where  month_of_attribution ${Date}  and ${Conract_var}) ,  expend as  (select sum(visit_amount) professionaL_expenditure  from L5.visit_patient vp  where  ${Conract_var}  and visit_start_date ${Date}  and visit_category = 'Professional' ) select round(professionaL_expenditure /member_months) as prof_pmpm  from attr, expend;

select CONCAT('$', ROUND(SUM(visit_amount) / 1000000, 1), 'M') from l5.network_leakage_patient t1 left join l5.pcp t2 on t1.org_hierarchy_master_id= t2.org_hierarchy_master_id left join l5.payer t3 on t1.payer_master_id= t3.payer_master_id where month_of_visit  ${Date}
and ${Conract_var} and visit_category='Professional'  and t1.out_of_network_flag=true ;

SELECT    CONCAT(     ROUND(       (SUM(CASE WHEN t1.out_of_network_flag = true THEN visit_amount ELSE 0 END)        / SUM(visit_amount)) ${default_file_name} 100, 1),      '%'   ) AS Leakage_Percentage  FROM l5.network_leakage_patient t1 LEFT JOIN l5.pcp t2   ON t1.org_hierarchy_master_id = t2.org_hierarchy_master_id LEFT JOIN l5.payer t3   ON t1.payer_master_id = t3.payer_master_id WHERE  month_of_visit  ${Date}
and ${Conract_var}   AND visit_category = 'Professional' ;

SELECT 
    CONCAT('$', ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN t1.out_of_network_flag = true 
                               AND sp.alternate_servicing_provider_npi1 IS NOT NULL 
                          THEN visit_amount ELSE 0 END) / 1000000, 1), 'M') AS Savings,
    CONCAT('$', ROUND(SUM(visit_amount) / 1000000, 1), 'M') AS Total_amount,
    ROUND( (SUM(CASE WHEN t1.out_of_network_flag = true 
                     AND sp.alternate_servicing_provider_npi1 IS NOT NULL 
                THEN visit_amount ELSE 0 END) 
           / SUM(visit_amount)) ${default_file_name} 100, 1) AS Potentially_Avoidable_Leakage_Percentage
FROM l5.visit_pcp t1
LEFT JOIN l5.pcp t2
ON t1.org_hierarchy_master_id = t2.org_hierarchy_master_id
LEFT JOIN l5.payer t3
ON t1.payer_master_id = t3.payer_master_id
LEFT JOIN l5.servicing_provider sp
ON t1.servicing_provider_npi = sp.servicing_provider_npi
WHERE month_of_visit  ${Date}
and ${Conract_var}
AND visit_category = 'Professional';
